    {
      "id": "5637a753-26b8-4935-a520-dc90248064a6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The goal of the paper is to create a predictive model that is able to predict final exam scores taking into consideration midterm exams.\n\nAuthors compare the performance of multiple different algorithms, SVM, RF, kNN, NB, etc… Sample includes data from a Turkish Language Course in the Fall of 2019/2020. Proposed model achievef 70 to 75% accuracy.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
